    "选中的 %lld 个应用包含 %lld 个 App Store 应用，迁移时会使用 Finder 删除，您会听到垃圾桶的声音。\n\n这是正常的，应用会被安全地移动到外部存储。" : {
      "extractionState" : "manual",
      "localizations" : {
        "ar" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "تتضمن التطبيقات المحددة %lld تطبيقًا %lld من App Store. سيتم حذفها عبر Finder (صوت سلة المهملات).\n\nهذا طبيعي."
          }
        },
        "br" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "⠠⠎⠑⠇⠑⠉⠞⠑⠙ %⠇⠇⠙ ⠁⠏⠏⠎ ⠊⠝⠉⠇⠥⠙⠑ %⠇⠇⠙ ⠠⠁⠏⠏ ⠠⠎⠞⠕⠗⠑ ⠁⠏⠏⠎⠲ ⠠⠞⠓⠑⠽ ⠺⠊⠇⠇ ⠃⠑ ⠙⠑⠇⠑⠞⠑⠙ ⠧⠊⠁ ⠠⠋⠊⠝⠙⠑⠗ ⠐⠣⠞⠗⠁⠎⠓ ⠎⠕⠥⠝⠙⠐⠜⠲\n\n⠠⠞⠓⠊⠎ ⠊⠎ ⠝⠕⠗⠍⠁⠇⠂ ⠁⠏⠏⠎ ⠁⠗⠑ ⠎⠁⠋⠑⠇⠽ ⠍⠕⠧⠑⠙⠲"
          }
        },
        "de" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Ausgewählte %lld Apps enthalten %lld App Store-Apps. Sie werden über den Finder gelöscht.\n\nDas ist normal."
          }
        },
        "en" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Selected %lld apps include %lld App Store apps. They will be deleted via Finder (trash sound).\n\nThis is normal, apps are safely moved."
          }
        },
        "eo" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Elektitaj %lld aplikaĵoj inkluzivas %lld App Store-aplikaĵojn. Ili estos forigitaj per Finder.\n\nĈi tio estas normala."
          }
        },
        "es" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Las %lld apps seleccionadas incluyen %lld de App Store. Se eliminarán vía Finder (sonido papelera).\n\nEs normal, se mueven con seguridad."
          }
        },
        "fr" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Les %lld apps sélectionnées incluent %lld apps App Store. Elles seront supprimées via Finder.\n\nC'est normal."
          }
        },
        "hi" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "चयनित %lld ऐप्स में %lld ऐप स्टोर ऐप्स शामिल हैं। उन्हें फाइंडर (कचरा ध्वनि) के माध्यम से हटा दिया जाएगा।\n\nयह सामान्य है, ऐप्स सुरक्षित रूप से स्थानांतरित हो जाते हैं।"
          }
        },
        "id" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Dipilih %lld aplikasi termasuk %lld aplikasi App Store. Mereka akan dihapus melalui Finder.\n\nIni normal."
          }
        },
        "it" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Le %lld app selezionate includono %lld app App Store. Verranno eliminate tramite Finder.\n\nÈ normale."
          }
        },
        "ja" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "選択された %lld 個のアプリには %lld 個のApp Storeアプリが含まれています。Finder経由で削除されます（ゴミ箱の音）。\n\nこれは正常です。"
          }
        },
        "ko" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "선택된 %lld개 앱에 %lld개의 App Store 앱이 포함되어 있습니다. Finder를 통해 삭제됩니다.\n\n이는 정상입니다."
          }
        },
        "nl" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Geselecteerde %lld apps bevatten %lld App Store-apps. Ze worden verwijderd via Finder.\n\nDit is normaal."
          }
        },
        "pl" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Wybrane aplikacje (%lld) zawierają aplikacje z App Store (%lld). Zostaną usunięte przez Finder.\n\nTo normalne."
          }
        },
        "pt" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Os %lld apps selecionados incluem %lld da App Store. Serão excluídos via Finder.\n\nIsso é normal."
          }
        },
        "ru" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Выбрано %lld приложений, включая %lld из App Store. Они будут удалены через Finder.\n\nЭто нормальный процесс."
          }
        },
        "th" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "แอปที่เลือก %lld รายการมีแอป App Store %lld รายการ จะถูกลบผ่าน Finder\n\nนี่เป็นเรื่องปกติ"
          }
        },
        "tr" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Seçilen %lld uygulama, %lld App Store uygulaması içeriyor. Finder aracılığıyla silinecekler.\n\nBu normaldir."
          }
        },
        "vi" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Đã chọn %lld ứng dụng bao gồm %lld ứng dụng App Store. Chúng sẽ bị xóa qua Finder.\n\nĐiều này là bình thường."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "选中的 %lld 个应用包含 %lld 个 App Store 应用，迁移时会使用 Finder 删除，您会听到垃圾桶的声音。\n\n这是正常的，应用会被安全地移动到外部存储。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hant" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "選中的 %lld 個應用程式包含 %lld 個 App Store 應用程式，遷移時會使用 Finder 刪除，您會聽到垃圾桶的聲音。\n\n這是正常的，應用程式會被安全地移動到外部儲存。"
