        "br" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "⠠⠊⠝⠎⠞⠁⠝⠞⠇⠽ ⠍⠕⠧⠑ ⠁⠏⠏⠎ ⠃⠁⠉⠅ ⠞⠕ ⠇⠕⠉⠁⠇ ⠌⠠⠁⠏⠏⠇⠊⠉⠁⠞⠊⠕⠝⠎ ⠺⠓⠑⠝⠑⠧⠑⠗ ⠝⠑⠑⠙⠑⠙⠲"
